WEBVTT

00:00.013 --> 00:01.995
Previously on Bates Motel...

00:01.996 --> 00:03.376
- Sheriff Romero?
- Yeah?

00:03.377 --> 00:05.233
- I'm Marcus Young.
- Running for sheriff.

00:05.234 --> 00:07.235
You want to do what's in the
best interest of the town?

00:07.236 --> 00:08.486
Find the damn flash drive.

00:08.487 --> 00:09.704
I didn't particularly want to bring

00:09.705 --> 00:10.788
Marcus Young out here to take your job.

00:10.789 --> 00:12.240
You left me with no choice.

00:12.241 --> 00:13.407
Someone ran you off the road?

00:13.408 --> 00:14.826
Yes, and threatened me.

00:14.827 --> 00:16.327
Call Mr. Paris.

00:16.328 --> 00:17.879
I found out that Norma's brother

00:17.880 --> 00:19.714
has been staying up at Dylan's farm.

00:19.715 --> 00:21.382
He raped her. He's dangerous.

00:21.383 --> 00:22.633
And I don't understand how Dylan

00:22.634 --> 00:23.751
could have anything to do with him.

00:23.752 --> 00:25.303
Because it's his father.

00:25.304 --> 00:26.587
Is it really like she said it was?

00:26.588 --> 00:28.139
Maybe not exactly.

00:28.140 --> 00:29.557
And Ma, we were so close, her and me.

00:29.558 --> 00:30.842
We were all we had.

00:30.843 --> 00:32.259
He just wants to talk to you, to tell you

00:32.261 --> 00:34.145
he's so sorry that it ever happened.

00:34.146 --> 00:35.513
You have to try and understand.

00:35.514 --> 00:37.732
It's his father.

00:37.733 --> 00:39.599
Mother, stop it! You're scaring me!

00:41.520 --> 00:43.570
Leave me the hell alone!

00:46.275 --> 00:49.827
Norman, let her go!

00:49.828 --> 00:52.112
Mother!

00:56.785 --> 00:59.754
Get her back, Dylan! Get her back!

00:59.755 --> 01:01.289
Calm down!

01:01.290 --> 01:03.791
Not calming down! She's never left me!

01:03.792 --> 01:05.092
Stop it!

01:05.093 --> 01:06.460
No!

01:06.461 --> 01:08.262
You have to! She's coming back!

01:08.263 --> 01:11.349
She's not gonna come back! She hates me!

01:11.350 --> 01:13.601
She hates me now, Dylan,
and it's all your fault!

01:13.602 --> 01:16.437
It's not my goddamn fault!

01:16.438 --> 01:18.438
Ah!

01:20.309 --> 01:23.360
Shit.

