34:14.237 --> 34:16.071
I'm just making some breakfast.

34:16.072 --> 34:18.456
French toast.

34:18.458 --> 34:19.491
Are you feeling better?

34:19.492 --> 34:21.159
Oh, I'm fine.

34:21.159 --> 34:23.462
Got some beautiful blackberries yesterday.

34:23.463 --> 34:24.629
Will you get them out of the fridge?

34:24.630 --> 34:26.496
Norman?

34:28.418 --> 34:31.168
Norman's sleeping.

34:31.170 --> 34:33.804
Get me the blackberries.
They're on the bottom shelf.

34:37.092 --> 34:39.511
Okay.

35:00.700 --> 35:03.418
- Can I help you?
- No, I'm fine.

35:03.419 --> 35:06.537
Maybe just go wake up your
brother, so he can eat.

35:08.207 --> 35:09.541
My brother?

35:09.542 --> 35:11.093
Yes, silly.

35:11.094 --> 35:13.461
What's wrong with you?

35:15.465 --> 35:16.715
Nothing's wrong with me.

35:16.716 --> 35:19.217
So run upstairs. You know how Norman is.

35:19.218 --> 35:22.636
He'll sleep all morning
if you don't wake him up.

35:56.143 --> 35:59.262
He's still sleeping?

35:59.263 --> 36:01.847
I hope he had a peaceful night.

36:03.484 --> 36:06.268
I'm gonna go home and shower and change.

36:08.272 --> 36:11.356
Thank you, Emma. I can't thank you enough.

36:13.577 --> 36:15.527
I'll be back soon.

37:02.576 --> 37:04.327
Hey.

37:04.328 --> 37:06.162
What are you doing?

37:06.163 --> 37:08.164
Um, I was...

37:08.165 --> 37:10.133
I'm going home. I have to go home.

37:10.134 --> 37:11.801
Jesus.

37:11.802 --> 37:15.254
Norma, okay, stop.

37:15.255 --> 37:17.340
Look, I-I know it doesn't seem like it,

37:17.341 --> 37:19.809
but you're in a very
fragile state right now.

37:19.810 --> 37:22.261
You need to stop worrying
about everybody else

37:22.262 --> 37:24.263
and just take care of yourself.

37:24.264 --> 37:26.766
I hear you, but I can't
take care of myself.

37:26.767 --> 37:28.768
I'm a mother.

37:28.769 --> 37:31.521
Now I have to go talk
to my horrible brother.

37:31.522 --> 37:32.822
You know what, I have no choice

37:32.823 --> 37:34.273
because it is important to my sons.

37:34.274 --> 37:36.442
Yeah, and what about your own needs?

37:36.443 --> 37:38.578
Parents do not have needs.

37:38.579 --> 37:40.530
You ever read the book The Giving Tree?

37:40.531 --> 37:43.116
It's about a tree, and
this kid keeps coming

37:43.117 --> 37:45.118
and taking stuff from it his whole life,

37:45.119 --> 37:47.286
until there's nothing left but a stump.

37:47.287 --> 37:49.372
And then the kid sits on the stump.

37:49.373 --> 37:52.174
That's being a parent.

38:06.473 --> 38:09.475
Morning, neighbor.

38:09.476 --> 38:11.476
Hey.

38:14.481 --> 38:16.481
What happened?

38:19.236 --> 38:22.155
Yeah.

38:22.156 --> 38:23.622
Okay.

38:25.626 --> 38:27.493
So I'm gonna leave.

38:27.494 --> 38:29.412
I just wanted to give you another shot

38:29.413 --> 38:31.413
at that driving gig.

38:35.636 --> 38:37.636
When's it happening?

38:39.173 --> 38:41.507
Couple of days.

38:41.508 --> 38:43.643
That work for you?

38:43.644 --> 38:45.811
Maybe. Yeah.

38:48.182 --> 38:50.233
What is it exactly?

38:50.234 --> 38:52.517
This "driving"?

38:54.354 --> 38:57.356
No need to worry about that now.

38:57.357 --> 38:58.775
When you need to know,

38:58.776 --> 39:02.744
I'll tell you.

39:17.344 --> 39:19.344
Wake up.

39:21.381 --> 39:24.300
- Norma?
- Wake up, Norman.

39:24.301 --> 39:25.551
- Mother.
- Come on.

39:25.552 --> 39:27.103
Get up. We got to go.

39:27.104 --> 39:28.554
Where are we going?

39:28.555 --> 39:30.306
We're going to the farm
to talk to your uncle.

39:30.307 --> 39:32.358
This might not be the best time.

39:32.359 --> 39:34.193
You don't have to. It... it was a bad idea.

39:34.194 --> 39:35.561
It doesn't matter. The damage is done.

39:35.562 --> 39:37.395
We're going.

39:42.569 --> 39:44.237
Why are we doing this?

39:44.238 --> 39:45.238
Because I said we're doing it.

39:45.239 --> 39:46.289
I don't want to go!

39:46.290 --> 39:48.291
Well, neither do I,

39:48.292 --> 39:49.575
but I'm not gonna be the mom who
says, "I won't talk to your dad

39:49.576 --> 39:51.661
because I hate him because he raped me."

39:51.662 --> 39:53.463
That's not what parents do.

39:53.464 --> 39:54.881
So get in the damn car!

40:03.757 --> 40:05.842
Why does she have this car?

40:05.843 --> 40:08.677
Look, don't ask any questions right now.

